Feature: Cyclos banking application

Scenario: Login page

Given User Launch the Application

When User click the login button

And User enter the username in the user name field

And User enter the password in the password field

Then User click the submit button and it navigates to dashboardpage

When User click the payuser button and it navigates to Payment to user page

And User click the Select the contact button the contact list will open

And User click the contact and it will added in To user menu

And User enter the amount in the amount field

And User click the Scheduling button and the Scheduling menu will open

And User click the Payuser button the payuser options will be selected

And User enter the Description in description menu

And User click the next button and it will navigates to payment confirmation page

And User click the confirm button and the payment will be paid to the person

